    <item>
      <title>欧洲国防股跳高领导人的军事支出承诺</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-03/european-defense-stocks-jump-as-leaders-show-support-for-ukraine</link>
      <description><![CDATA[欧洲国防股提高了，对该地区较高支出的乐观情绪增加了约300亿美元的市值。法国的CAC 40指数短暂超过了其5月的纪录量，而汽车制造商在评论说，他们将在达到排放目标方面有所余地。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-03/european-defense-stocks-jump-as-leaders-show-support-for-ukraine</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 03 Mar 2025 07:09:50 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>随着投资者的紧张关税，信用量正在破裂</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-03/credit-spreads-are-on-their-longest-widening-streak-since-2023</link>
      <description><![CDATA[全球公司债券的差额已连续进行八次交易，结束了一段显着宁静的时期，因为投资者对关税的影响感到担忧，因此开始防御。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-03/credit-spreads-are-on-their-longest-widening-streak-since-2023</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 03 Mar 2025 02:44:41 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
